It looks different than it used to but there is no one else I’d rather have by my side as we navigate adulting, parenting, practice schedules, dance classes, work, volunteering at school, car pools, self care, working out, sleep and all the other stuff were are supposed to do in a day, all without losing our s#*@ daily trying to keep it all together. I love you and the perfectly crazy little trio angels/monsters that we call children. 🤪💕

Happy 7th birthday Henry!!! 💙 You’ve kept us on our toes from the second you were born, and we could not love you more. You have the sweetest smile, and an even kinder little heart.  You are our silly, super smart, sports loving little buddy and we love you more than you love Fortnite and video games (and that’s a lot)!

Today we celebrated FOUR years of loving this sweet little princess! 💕 The last four years have gone by in a blur and although I miss the sweet, chubby little baby you were, I love watching you grow into the sweet, strong, fearless little girl that you are becoming! 💜 Caroline Olivia you are everything we wanted in a little girl and we couldn’t love you more!! Happy birthday pretty girl!
